        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",

      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "df=pd.read_csv(\"/content/Auto.csv\")\n",

        "\n",

        "df_sub[\"horsepower\"]=pd.to_numeric(df_sub[\"horsepower\"],errors=\"coerce\")\n",
        "df_sub=df_sub.dropna(axis=0)\n",

        "y=df_sub[\"mpg\"]\n",

        "model=sm.OLS(y,X).fit()\n",

        "print(\"Critical Values:\",result[4][\"10%\"])"

        "q=log.values\n",
        "delta_q=np.diff(q)\n",
        "q_lag=q[:-1]\n",
        "P=sm.add_constant(q_lag)\n",
        "model_1=sm.OLS(delta_q,P).fit()\n",
        "lambda_hat=model_1.params[1]\n",
        "halflife=(-1)*np.log(2)/lambda_hat\n",
        "print(\"Halflife:\",halflife)"
